        "name": [
          "Can we monitor User Happiness on the Web with performance tools?"
        ],
        "url": [
          "https://nicolas-hoizey.com/articles/2020/01/10/can-we-monitor-user-happiness-on-the-web-with-performance-tools/"
        ],
        "author": [
